Title: Series: Theatrum Artis Pictoriae
Description: The flight into Egypt with at the centre of a landscape the Virgin and child on a donkey guided by St Joseph; nearby, two sleeping putti; after Domenico Fetti. 1728 Etching
Producer name: Print made by: Anton Joseph Prenner
Dimensions: Width: 216 millimetres (sheet size (trimmed within plate mark))
